Title: Tescom Collagen
Body (HTML): TESCOM - the number one professional hair dryer brand in Japan, came out with the newest technology and first in the world - beauty collagen hair dryer to promote healthy hair growth and protect hair scalp What actually is Beauty Collagen Collagen is one of the most abundant protein in our body, making up a large part of our skin, hair, and nails. While collagen is beneficial to our skin, which gives strength and elasticity, it is also beneficial to our hair. Each bulb of hair on our head is surrounded by sheath of collagen. That's where it connects to micro-vessels that deliver necessary nutrients for our hair. Therefore, the collagen in our hair is a vital component to determine our hair's thickness, elasticity, and smoothness. Once our hair is lack of collagen, it will cause our hair to be a dry, frizzy hair with split ends.

As a former competitive endurance athlete (finishing 5th place USA Marathon Championship, 4th place Hawaii Ironman), Mark lost both health and vitality through an oppressive training regimen and highly inflammatory diet. After taking up ancestral eating, he was blown away with the dramatic shift and improvement in his overall health and enjoyment for life by simply changing the way he ate. Primal Kitchen is committed to the highest quality ingredients with products that are free of dairy, gluten, grains, refined sugar, soy and industrial seed oils (like canola, sunflower or safflower). Primal Kitchen founder, Mark Sisson, reminds us to Eat Like Your Life Depends On It. Body (HTML): The Pause Collagen Boosting Moisturizer helps hydrate, add volume, firm, lift, brighten aging skin. Key benefits of the Pause Collagen Boosting Moisturizer include: Niacinamide: This ingredient knows how to multitask. A form of vitamin B3, used to calm skin and promote collagen production while preventing signs of age. 3-O-Ethyl Ascorbic Acid: This stable vitamin C derivative protects skin from UVB damage, enhances collagen synthesis, and helps brighten uneven skin tone. Poria Cocos Polysaccharide: Skin-soothing antioxidant, derived from mushrooms helps increase skin thickness and density, which is key for aging and menopausal skin. Ribose: Found in all living cells, its the only cosmetic ingredient that restores skin cell energy, for improved skin tone and cell function.
